00:25:50,017 --> 00:25:52,017
Tri!

413
00:25:52,017 --> 00:25:54,017
Dobre.

414
00:25:54,440 --> 00:25:56,839
Raz. Dva.

415
00:25:56,839 --> 00:25:58,068
- Silnejšie.
